memberdef.name: RETURN_CHECK
memberdef.initializer: do { \ const xAOD::TReturnCode result = EXP; \ if( ! result.isSuccess() ) { \ ::Error( CONTEXT, XAOD_MESSAGE( "Failed to execute: %s" ), \ #EXP ); \ return 1; \ } \ } while( false )

memberdef.name: SIMPLE_ASSERT
memberdef.initializer: do { \ const bool result = EXP; \ if( ! result ) { \ ::Error( CONTEXT, \ XAOD_MESSAGE( "Expression \"%s\" failed the evaluation" ), \ #EXP ); \ return 1; \ } \ } while( 0 )

briefdescription.para: Helper macro for evaluating logical tests.
